      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Twin Sparks in the Dark",
        "Client": "Jungle Observation Member",
        "Description": "A pair of Zinogre in the Jungle,\r\nover! What a menace, over!\r\nLightning so bright, you\r\nwouldn\u0027t think it was night,\r\nover! Potential threat to the\r\nsurrounding villages, over!\r\nHunt them at once, over and out!",
